verbose_text: It has also been found to be highly enriched in the ureteric bud tip compared with the ureteric stalk, and to be one of the most highly induced targets of GDNF signaling in the mouse ureteric bud (embryonic day 11.5) (and GUDMAP confirms its expression at this time as well as being strongly expressed specifically in the ureteric tip on day 15.5) so it is a good candidate.
